### Sales Flow (`src/components/sales-flow/`)
- `decision-tree.tsx` — Central orchestrator (7 steps, auto-save, contact gating, `variant="drawer"` for embedded use, dynamic `continueLabel`, timestamped question/objection tracking, fetches `storeSubdomain` on mount, single-select discovery categories, sample quantities tracking)
- `step-add-contact.tsx` — Step 1: create contact + select products (gate)
- `step-rapport.tsx` — Step 2: single conversational transcript with [Name] personalization (no product pills); talking points, transition bridge to discovery (read-only, no persisted state)
- `step-discovery-v2.tsx` — Step 3: 5 universal discovery questions (single category select, quality rating 1-10, duration, what they've tried, results)
- `step-send-samples.tsx` — Step 4: 2-script sample flow (offer, "special gift" commitment) + product picker with per-product quantity stepper + address
- `step-followup.tsx` — Step 5: follow-up sequence (shipping, arrival+checkbox, Liberty special gift reveal, per-product experience check-ins, results follow-up, reorder+referral, ask for the close); dynamically expands check-in steps when multiple products sent
- `step-close.tsx` — Step 6: closing techniques + collapsible objection handling (merged)
- `step-purchase-links.tsx` — Step 7: branded product business card (primary share via image+URL) + text scripts (secondary) + Won/Lost outcome recording
- `product-tabs.tsx` — Multi-product tabbed content
- `customer-insight.tsx` — Customer profile from roadmap

