## Sales Step IDs (in order)

`add_contact` → `rapport` → `discovery` → `samples` → `followup` → `close` → `purchase_links`

## Database Table: `d2c_contacts`

Key columns: `user_id`, `product_ids text[]`, `first_name`, `last_name`, `email`, `phone`, address fields, `current_step`, `stage_entered_at`, `opening_types jsonb`, `questions_asked jsonb`, `objections_encountered jsonb`, `closing_techniques jsonb`, `sample_sent`, `sample_sent_at`, `sample_products text[]`, `sample_quantities jsonb`, `sample_followup_done`, `outcome`, `follow_up_day`, `bydesign_customer_did`, `bydesign_matched_at`, `bydesign_match_confidence` (email | phone | name | manual), `bydesign_order_count`, `bydesign_total_spent`

## Database Table: `user_profiles` (onboarding columns)

Key additions: `onboarding_step text` (carousel | tour | checklist | completed), `onboarding_checklist jsonb` (5 boolean milestone flags), `store_subdomain text` (MLM store subdomain for purchase URLs), `notification_preferences jsonb` (follow_up_reminders, overdue_alerts, sample_check_ins booleans), `social_links jsonb` (partial record of social platform handles: instagram, facebook, tiktok, youtube, linkedin, x), `bydesign_rep_did text` (ByDesign Rep ID), `bydesign_api_username text`, `bydesign_api_key_encrypted bytea` (pgcrypto encrypted), `bydesign_connected_at timestamptz`, `bydesign_rank text`

## Database Table: `d2c_activity_log`

Append-only event log for unified activity feed. Key columns: `user_id`, `contact_id`, `event_type` (contact_created | step_changed | sample_sent | sample_confirmed | followup_completed | outcome_changed | invite_sent | member_joined | purchase_matched | downline_synced), `metadata` (jsonb), `created_at`. RLS scoped to `auth.uid() = user_id`. Events logged fire-and-forget from server actions.

## Database Table: `d2c_push_subscriptions`

Key columns: `user_id`, `endpoint`, `p256dh`, `auth` — stores web push subscriptions per user with RLS

## Database Table: `d2c_downline_cache`

ByDesign downline per leader. Key columns: `leader_id`, `rep_did`, `rep_name`, `email`, `rank`, `level`, `pv`, `gv`, `rep_status`, `star_user_id`, `invite_token`, `invite_status` (not_invited | invited | accepted | declined), `synced_at`. RLS scoped to `auth.uid() = leader_id`.

## Database Table: `d2c_team_members`

Linked S.T.A.R. team members. Key columns: `leader_id`, `member_id`, `member_rep_did`, `level`, `joined_at`. RLS: leaders see their members, members see their own membership row.

## Database Table: `d2c_purchase_matches`

Matched ByDesign orders to contacts. Key columns: `user_id`, `contact_id`, `bydesign_customer_did`, `bydesign_order_id`, `order_date`, `order_total`, `products_purchased` (jsonb). RLS scoped to `auth.uid() = user_id`.

## Environment Variables

`NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY` (push notifications), `VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY` (push, server-side only), `CRON_SECRET` (Vercel Cron auth), `BYDESIGN_API_BASE_URL`, `BYDESIGN_API_USERNAME`, `BYDESIGN_API_PASSWORD` (dev/test shared creds), `BYDESIGN_ENCRYPTION_KEY` (pgcrypto symmetric key)

## Conventions

- Use **shadcn/ui** components for all UI
- Use **Server Actions** (not API routes) for data mutations
- All files go in `src/` — never create files at project root
- Product pages are reference-only; sales flow lives inside the contact drawer on `/contacts`
- Roadmap JSON files are the single source of truth for sales scripts
- **Every user-facing script/text** must have a `ShareCopyButton` (from `src/components/ui/share-copy-button.tsx`) — uses Web Share API on mobile, falls back to clipboard copy on desktop
- Update `README.md` before every commit
